summary: So my friend was driving us to work on a Wednesday arvo, music is playing from her phone and we're talking about what's happened...
body:
So my friend was driving us to work on a Wednesday arvo, music is playing from her phone and we’re talking about what’s happened the last time we saw each other (which was like 3 days ago 😂)

So I started telling her story about my mum and I as the song finishes….

The intro of IKYWT starts playing and I just stop telling her my story

And she’s says “are you going finish your story?”

Waving her hand dismissively. “Nevermind I get it. It’s Taylor Swift.”

As I proceed singing the whole song beginning to end.😄

This is why I’m friends with this amazing person.
